    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The exterior has some visible scratches and minor dings, and the interior shows signs of regular use with some wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it starts and runs, but it may require some upcoming maintenance like new tires or a brake service to keep it in peak operating shape. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for an affordable, functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
