    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable and character-filled ride! While it shows some honest signs of use and age, it remains a solid performer that\u2019s ready to get you where you need to go reliably. It\u2019s the perfect choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle at a great value. Come see its potential for yourself!",
