    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical market offering. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior profile and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering the discerning collector a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine automobile. This is not merely a pre-owned vehicle; it is a preserved legacy of automotive excellence.",
