    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that defines the term 'showroom condition.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its original luster and factory-fresh appeal. The exterior paint is deep and mirror-like, free from any stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin remains a time capsule; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and all tactile surfaces still retain their factory matte finish. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history detailing preventative maintenance that exceeds manufacturer standards. Every switch, button, and electronic feature operates with the crisp precision of a new vehicle. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen for the most discerning enthusiast who refuses to compromise on quality.",
